Create brows like a pro! @slaybyjess shows us how to perfect your shape using Brow Wiz in Dark Brown.
 
The Golden Ratio Method:
 
✨Start of the Brow:
Align your pencil vertically from the center of your nostril up—this is where your brow should begin.
 
✨End of the Brow:
Angle the pencil from the bottom outer corner of your nostril to the outer corner of your eye—this is where your brow should end.
 
✨Arch of the Brow:
Looking straight ahead, place the pencil from the tip of your nose through the center of your iris—this marks your natural arch.
 
#ABHBrows #AnastasiaBeverlyHills
